{"id":148810,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/《arnold专栏》投资者看多中国同时-亦寻找风险对冲途/","date":"2011-04-28T14:04:00Z","modified":"2011-04-28T14:04:00Z","title":"《Arnold专栏》投资者看多中国同时 亦寻找风险对冲途径","content":"<p>路透香港4月27日电&#8212;投资者正在寻找对冲中国风险的完美途径.虽然廉价的美元正大量涌入中国,以及受益于该国快速增长的其他亚洲经济体,但随着中国通胀的上升,投资者正愈发担心其经济可能过热,并正在为可能出现的变故寻求保护.<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cn.reuters.feedsportal.com/c/33087/f/535380/s/14791c95/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E3%80%8AArnold%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E3%80%8B%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%80%85%E7%9C%8B%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6+%E4%BA%A6%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%B2%E9%80%94%E5%BE%84&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FcolumnistNews%2FidCNCHINA-4217220110428%3FfeedType%3DRSS%26feedName%3DcolumnistNews\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/04/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E3%80%8AArnold%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E3%80%8B%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%80%85%E7%9C%8B%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6+%E4%BA%A6%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%B2%E9%80%94%E5%BE%84&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FcolumnistNews%2FidCNCHINA-4217220110428%3FfeedType%3DRSS%26feedName%3DcolumnistNews\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/04/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101090832049/u/31/f/535380/c/33087/s/14791c95/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101090832049/u/31/f/535380/c/33087/s/14791c95/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cn.reuters.feedsportal.com/c/33087/f/535380/s/14791c95/mf.gif\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期